RESTRICT

Test: CONTROL
Utility: Validate
Usage:  ^gRESTRICT <test/detection> <icon>^n

This operation is used to interfere with an icon, either by inhibiting it's
operations or raising it's detection factor. It can only be used against
other deckers you have located. The oposing icon's detection factor is
added to the control test.

^wSee Also: UTILITIES^n
